{"word":"G1704 - ἐμπεριπατέω - emperipatéō - em-per-ee-pat-eh'-o - Walk in","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμπεριπατέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">emperipatéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em-per-ee-pat-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Walk in</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உலாவு"},{"paragraph":"to go about in, walk in"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G4043 - περιπατέω - peripatéō - per-ee-pat-eh'-o/4043\">G4043</a>; to <i>perambulate on</i> a place, that is, (figuratively) to <i>be occupied among</i> persons: - walk in.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1704/1704\">G1704</a>, <a href=\"#/G2662/2662\">G2662</a>, <a href=\"#/G3961/3961\">G3961</a>, <a href=\"#/G4043/4043\">G4043</a>"}]}